{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775877768701,"sessionID":"ses_285712c33ffeKLPVuYWhDtZwf2","part":{"id":"prt_d7a9045d8001Tb8FpT1oDHLTdq","messageID":"msg_d7a90279f0016rpm5TT7i0rb5h","sessionID":"ses_285712c33ffeKLPVuYWhDtZwf2","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-8dcc475853db4a91a278ff4229bc996e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: \n5: | 属性 | 值 |\n6: |------|-----|\n7: | AR | AR-023 |\n8: | Module | cmd/cli |\n9: | Language | Python |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## 1. Purpose (目的)\n15: \n16: 实现 AgentCube CLI 的 `invoke` 和 `status` 命令，用于调用已发布的 agent 并查询其运行状态。这两个命令是 agent 生命周期管理的关键组成部分，让开发者能够验证 agent 的正确部署并与之交互。\n17: \n18: **Current State**: 当前 CLI 已实现 `pack`、`build`、`publish` 命令，完成 agent 的打包、构建和部署流程，但缺少调用和状态查询能力。\n19: \n20: **Target State**: \n21: 1. `invoke` 命令: POST JSON payload 到已发布 agent 的 endpoint，支持自定义 headers，自动处理 AgentRuntime CR 的 URL 重写\n22: 2. `status` 命令: 加载 workspace metadata 并以 Rich Table 展示 agent 状态，支持 agentcube 和 k8s provider\n23: \n24: ---\n25: \n26: ## 2. Scope (范围)\n27: \n28: ### 2.1 In Scope\n29: \n30: **invoke 命令**\n31: - Typer CLI 命令定义与参数\n32: - payload JSON 解析与验证\n33: - header_list 解析（key:value 格式）\n34: - workspace 路径处理与 metadata 加载\n35: - provider 选择（agentcube/k8s）\n36: - session_id header 注入\n37: - URL 重写：AgentRuntime CR → `{router}/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/`\n38: - 直接 HTTP 调用（k8s provider）\n39: - async HTTP 请求处理\n40: - 响应输出与错误处理\n41: \n42: **status 命令**\n43: - Typer CLI 命令定义与参数\n44: - workspace 路径处理与 metadata 加载\n45: - provider 选择（agentcube/k8s）\n46: - Kubernetes CR status 查询\n47: - Kubernetes Deployment/Service status 查询\n48: - Rich Table 状态展示\n49: - 状态判断：not_published/error → exit code 1\n50: \n51: **Runtime 类**\n52: - `InvokeRuntime` (`agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py`)\n53:   - `invoke()` 方法\n54:   - `_validate_invoke_prerequisites()` 前置检查\n55:   - `_invoke_agent_via_agentcube()` AgentRuntime CR 调用\n56:   - `_direct_http_invocation()` 直接 HTTP 调用\n57: - `StatusRuntime` (`agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py`)\n58:   - `get_status()` 方法\n59:   - `_get_k8s_status()` K8s Deployment/Service 状态\n60:   - `_get_cr_k8s_status()` AgentRuntime CR 状态\n61: \n62: ### 2.2 Out of Scope\n63: \n64: - Python SDK (`sdk-python`) 的 AgentRuntimeClient（已有独立实现）\n65: - Code Interpreter 相关功能\n66: - WebSocket 或 streaming 调用模式\n67: - 批量 invoke 操作\n68: - invoke 结果的持久化存储\n69: \n70: ---\n71: \n72: ## 3. Impact Analysis (影响分析)\n73: \n74: ### 3.1 新增文件\n75: \n76: ```\n77: cmd/cli/\n78: ├ agentcube/\n79: │   ├── runtime/\n80: │   │   ├── invoke_runtime.py     # InvokeRuntime 类实现\n81: │   │   └── status_runtime.py     # StatusRuntime 类实现\n82: │   └── cli/\n83: │       └── main.py               # 添加 invoke/status 命令（修改）\n84: ├ tests/\n85: │   ├── test_invoke_runtime.py    # InvokeRuntime 单元测试\n86: │   └── test_status_runtime.py    # StatusRuntime 单元测试\n87: ```\n88: \n89: ### 3.2 修改文件\n90: \n91: | 文件 | 修改内容 |\n92: |------|----------|\n93: | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | 添加 invoke/status 命令函数 |\n94: | `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | 导出 InvokeRuntime, StatusRuntime |\n95: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | 导出 InvokeRuntime（可选） |\n96: \n97: ### 3.3 依赖关系\n98: \n99: ```toml\n100: # 新增依赖（用于 async HTTP）\n101: dependencies = [\n102:     # ... existing ...\n103:     \"httpx>=0.24.0\",  # 已存在，用于 async HTTP\n104: ]\n105: ```\n106: \n107: ### 3.4 与现有模块交互\n108: \n109: | 模块 | 交互方式 |\n110: |------|----------|\n111: | `agentcube.cli.main` | invoke/status 命令入口，调用对应 Runtime |\n112: | `agentcube.runtime.invoke_runtime` | 调用 MetadataService 加载 metadata |\n113: | `agentcube.runtime.status_runtime` | 调用 KubernetesProvider/AgentCubeProvider |\n114: | `agentcube.services.k8s_provider` | 查询 Deployment/Service 状态 |\n115: | `agentcube.services.agentcube_provider` | 查询 AgentRuntime CR 状态 |\n116: \n117: ### 3.5 风险与缓解\n118: \n119: | 风险 | 影响 | 缓解措施 |\n120: |------|------|----------|\n121: | agent endpoint 缺失 | High | 前置检查 metadata.agent_endpoint，提示用户先 publish |\n122: | Kubernetes 连接失败 | Medium | k8s provider 初始化时检查 kubeconfig，提供清晰错误信息 |\n123: | JSON payload 无效 | Low | invoke 命令入口即验证 JSON，不传递到 Runtime |\n124: | header 格式错误 | Low | invoke 命令入口验证 header 格式 |\n125: | AgentRuntime CR URL 重写错误 | Medium | 根据 k8s_deployment.type 判断，fallback 到直接 endpoint |\n126: \n127: ---\n128: \n129: ## 4. Alternatives Considered (备选方案)\n130: \n131: ### 4.1 invoke 实现：async vs sync\n132: \n133: **方案 A: async httpx（推荐）**\n134: - 优点：高性能、支持 timeout 控制、与 SDK 设计一致\n135: - 缺点：需要 asyncio.run() 包装\n136: \n137: **方案 B: sync requests**\n138: - 优点：简单直接\n139: - 缺点：性能较差、与 SDK 设计不一致\n140: \n141: **决策**: 采用方案 A，使用 async httpx，与 Python SDK 的 `AgentRuntimeClient` 保持一致\n142: \n143: ### 4.2 status 输出格式\n144: \n145: **方案 A: Rich Table（推荐）**\n146: - 优点：美观、结构化、支持颜色标记状态\n147: - 缺点：不适合管道处理\n148: \n149: **方案 B: JSON 输出**\n150: - 优点：可管道化、便于脚本处理\n151: - 缺点：用户体验差\n152: \n153: **方案 C: 两者都支持**\n154: - 优点：灵活性高\n155: - 缺点：增加复杂度\n156: \n157: **决策**: 采用方案 A，默认 Rich Table；未来可扩展 `--format json` 选项\n158: \n159: ### 4.3 provider 参数处理\n160: \n161: **方案 A: 继承 metadata 中的 provider 配置（推荐）**\n162: - 优点：减少用户输入、与 publish 流程一致\n163: - 缺点：可能需要从 k8s_deployment 推断\n164: \n165: **方案 B: 强制用户指定**\n166: - 优点：明确、避免歧义\n167: - 缺点：增加用户负担\n168: \n169: **决策**: 采用方案 A，默认从 metadata.k8s_deployment.type 推断，支持 CLI --provider 覆盖\n170: \n171: ### 4.4 invoke endpoint URL 构建\n172: \n173: **方案 A: 根据 provider 自动重写（推荐）**\n174: - AgentRuntime CR: `{router_url}/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/`\n175: - K8s: 直接使用 `agent_endpoint`\n176: - 优点：简化用户操作\n177: \n178: **方案 B: 用户手动指定完整 URL**\n179: - 优点：完全灵活\n180: - 缺点：用户负担重\n181: \n182: **决策**: 采用方案 A，自动构建 URL，提供 --endpoint 覆盖选项\n183: \n184: ---\n185: \n186: ## 5. 设计要点\n187: \n188: ### 5.1 invoke 命令参数\n189: \n190: ```python\n191: def invoke(\n192:     workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", help=\"Path to the agent workspace directory\", show_default=True),\n193:     payload: str = typer.Option(\"{}\", \"--payload\", help=\"JSON-formatted input passed to the agent\"),\n194:     header_list: Optional[List[str]] = typer.Option(None, \"--header\", help=\"Custom HTTP headers (e.g., 'Authorization: Bearer token'). Can be specified multiple times.\"),\n195:     provider: str = typer.Option(\"agentcube\", \"--provider\", help=\"Target provider: 'agentcube' (AgentRuntime CR) or 'k8s' (Deployment/Service)\"),\n196:     verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", help=\"Enable detailed logging\"),\n197: ) -> None:\n198: ```\n199: \n200: ### 5.2 status 命令参数\n201: \n202: ```python\n203: def status(\n204:     workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", help=\"Path to the agent workspace directory\", show_default=True),\n205:     provider: str = typer.Option(\"agentcube\", \"--provider\", help=\"Target provider: 'agentcube' (AgentRuntime CR) or 'k8s' (Deployment/Service)\"),\n206:     verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", help=\"Enable detailed logging\"),\n207: ) -> None:\n208: ```\n209: \n210: ### 5.3 InvokeRuntime 核心方法\n211: \n212: ```python\n213: class InvokeRuntime:\n214:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \"agentcube\") -> None: ...\n215:     def invoke(self, workspace_path: Path, payload: Dict[str, Any], headers: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None) -> Any: ...\n216:     def _validate_invoke_prerequisites(self, workspace_path: Path) -> Tuple[AgentMetadata, str, str]: ...\n217:     async def _invoke_agent_via_agentcube(self, agent_id: str, payload: Dict[str, Any], headers: Optional[Dict[str, str]], endpoint: str, workspace_path: Path) -> Any: ...\n218:     async def _direct_http_invocation(self, endpoint: str, payload: Dict[str, Any], headers: Optional[Dict[str, str]], workspace_path: Path) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n219: ```\n220: \n221: ### 5.4 StatusRuntime 核心方法\n222: \n223: ```python\n224: class StatusRuntime:\n225:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \"agentcube\") -> None: ...\n226:     def get_status(self, workspace_path: Path, provider: Optional[str] = None) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n227:     def _get_k8s_status(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n228:     def _get_cr_k8s_status(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n229: ```\n230: \n231: ### 5.5 成功输出示例\n232: \n233: **invoke**:\n234: ```\n235: [green]Invocation successful[/green]\n236: Response: {\"result\": \"Hello, World!\", \"status\": \"completed\"}\n237: ```\n238: \n239: **status**:\n240: ```\n241: ┌─────────────┬──────────────┬────────────┬──────────┐\n242: │ Field       │ Value        │ Status     │ Provider │\n243: ├─────────────┼──────────────┼────────────┼──────────┤\n244: │ Agent Name  │ my-agent     │ running    │ agentcube│\n245: │ Agent ID    │ abc123       │            │          │\n246: │ Endpoint    │ http://...   │            │          │\n247: │ Namespace   │ default      │            │          │\n248: │ Replicas    │ 1/1          │            │          │\n249: └─────────────┴──────────────┴────────────┴──────────┘\n250: ```\n251: \n252: ### 5.6 状态类型\n253: \n254: | 状态值 | 描述 | Exit Code |\n255: |--------|------|-----------|\n256: | `running` | Agent 正常运行 | 0 |\n257: | `created_no_status` | CR 已创建但无 status | 0 |\n258: | `not_published` | metadata 无 agent_id | 1 |\n259: | `error` | 状态显示错误 | 1 |\n260: | `not_found_in_k8s` | K8s 资源未找到 | 1 |\n261: \n262: ---\n263: \n264: ## 6. 实施计划\n265: \n266: | 阶段 | 内容 | 预估工时 |\n267: |------|------|----------|\n268: | P1 | InvokeRuntime 基础框架 + _validate_invoke_prerequisites | 1d |\n269: | P2 | async HTTP invoke 实现 + session header 处理 | 1d |\n270: | P3 | StatusRuntime 基础框架 + provider 状态查询 | 1d |\n271: | P4 | CLI 命令集成 + Rich Table 输出 | 1d |\n272: | P5 | 单元测试 + 错误处理完善 | 1d |\n273: \n274: **总计**: ~5 人天\n275: \n276: ---\n277: \n278: ## 7. 参考文档\n279: \n280: - cli-toolkit/design.md: CLI 设计文档\n281: - cli-toolkit/spec.md: CLI 规范文档\n282: - python-sdk/design.md: SDK AgentRuntimeClient 设计\n283: - python-sdk/spec.md: SDK 规范\n284: - changes/AR-020/proposal.md: pack 命令 proposal\n285: - agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py: Kubernetes 状态查询实现\n286: - agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py: AgentCube CR 状态查询实现\n\n(End of file - total 286 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令\n\n## 概述\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| AR | AR-023 |\n| Module | cmd/cli |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n\n---\n\n## 1. Purpose (目的)\n\n实现 AgentCube CLI 的 `invoke` 和 `status` 命令，用于调用已发布的 agent 并查询其运行状态。这两个命令是 agent 生命周期管理的关键组成部分，让开发者能够验证 agent 的正确部署并与之交互。\n\n**Current State**: 当前 CLI 已实现 `pack`、`build`、`publish` 命令，完成 agent 的打包、构建和部署流程，但缺少调用和状态查询能力。\n\n**Target State**: ","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775877768683,"end":1775877768698}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775877768728,"sessionID":"ses_285712c33ffeKLPVuYWhDtZwf2","part":{"id":"prt_d7a9045fc001oRwsLT0j5Em7yP","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d7a90279f0016rpm5TT7i0rb5h","sessionID":"ses_285712c33ffeKLPVuYWhDtZwf2","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":34843,"input":19677,"output":63,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":15103}},"cost":0}}
